ife of  Henry VI  of England,  Margaret of Anjou  (  1430–82 ), and of  Margaret Tudor  (  1489–1541 ), sister of  Henry VIII , who married James IV of Scotland and ruled as regent there after his death.  See also  Margery  ,   Marjorie ."],"variants":[{"name":"Margareta","meanings":["From the Latin form of Greek <i>Margarītēs</i>.  See  <b>Margaret</b>   ."]},{"name":"Margaretta","meanings":["Formed from Margaret."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Margaret deHarley was born about 1380, in Monmouthshire, Wales, United Kingdom as the daughter of deHarley. She married Richard Rhys Moythe in 1417, in Monmouthshire, Wales, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. She died in her hometown."},"et":{"Abt. 1380–":"umbes 1380–Surnud","1380–Female":"1380–Surnud","1380–Male":"1380–Surnud","1417–1443":"1417–1443","–Male":"Surnud","Abt. 1380":"umbes 1380","1443":"1443","1380":"1380","1417":"1417","Maelor Gymraeg, Wrexham district, Denbigh, Wales":"Wrexham, Denbighshire, Wales, United Kingdom","Monmouthshire, Wales":"Monmouthshire, Wales, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt. 1380–":"noin 1380–Kuollut","1380–Female":"1380–Kuollut","1380–Male":"1380–Kuollut","1417–1443":"1417–1443","–Male":"Kuollut","Abt. 1380":"noin 1380","1443":"1443","1380":"1380","1417":"1417","Maelor Gymraeg, Wrexham district, Denbigh, Wales":"Wrexham, Denbighshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Monmouthshire, Wales":"Monmouthshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt. 1380–":"environ 1380–Décédée","1380–Female":"1380–Décédée","1380–Male":"1380–Décédé","1417–1443":"1417–1443","–Male":"Décédé","Abt. 1380":"environ 1380","1443":"1443","1380":"1380","1417":"1417","Maelor Gymraeg, Wrexham district, Denbigh, Wales":"Wrexham, Denbighshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","Monmouthshire, Wales":"Monmouthshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Margaret deHarley est née environ 1380, à Monmouthshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni, fille de deHarley. Elle a épousé Richard Rhys Moythe en 1417, à Monmou